          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Weird western fans, fantasy fans, Dark Tower fans</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/35127081-ashe-armstrong?shelf=weird-west">weird-west</a>
