<div id="review_938111506" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/938111506" />
    <a title="Dava Stewart" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4971565-dava-stewart"><img alt="Dava Stewart" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1298049304p2/4971565.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/938111506?book_show_action=true">May 15, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dava Stewart" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dava Stewart" href="/user/show/4971565-dava-stewart">Dava Stewart</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/17840141-the-whirlwind-in-the-thorn-tree">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer938111506" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14515820022799307141">I quite liked the first book in this series, and must say, this one is better. The writing is tighter, and we get to learn a little more about the characters. <br/><br/>Looking forward to the third one. </span>

          </span>
